{"tid":2343736,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專家證人相信閉路電視片段「光影」屬周梓樂墮下情況","createTime":"2020-12-28T07:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T07:08:30.000Z","uid":21470,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c3283215393cded931b39de50f265bb7c9376fb9","tid":2343736,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"專家證人相信閉路電視片段「光影」屬周梓樂墮下情況<br />\n<br />\n科大學生周梓樂死因研訊第22日，專家證人綜合多個閉路電視片段，指尚德停車場2樓一個閉路電視在凌晨1時01分拍攝到一道光影，根據調查，相信當時是拍攝到周梓樂從3樓墮下的情況。<br />\n<br />\n專家證人、政府高級化驗師鄭郁棋表示，周梓樂身高1.75米，他曾用一個1.8米高的人偶，模擬從3樓墮下到2樓的情況，發現透過閉路電視影像，有物件墮下會形成一道光影。他解釋，由於閉路電視會壓縮影像，若物件快速墮下，拍攝的影像會變得模糊，形成光影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567446-20201228.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567446-20201228.htm&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdxQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=8f24e762\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567446-20201228.htm&h=762854c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567446-20201228.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4261bf2305c2949364ac52b31a8694e0b0af60f1","tid":2343736,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:22:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b46f6c20a12a1cbe1950f64b8cf6c8792a24320","tid":2343736,"uid":33398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:27:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09ec6866026e7ac877eeb90febe49d862ba3a7a7","tid":2343736,"uid":295893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:27:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88993e4cbeacbdc42fda7be4d5512ed6be513000","tid":2343736,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\"